data.description: If you're looking for Oxford school district and a close to perfect family home, look no further. This is a child friendly subdivision with a double lot. Just a couple of years ago the home has been boasted of updates. Privacy galore, the family room overlooks the deck and fenced in back yard. Almost an acre of land- you will want to call today to set a viewing. Won't last long.
